TTF/Ruby
========

    TTF/Ruby is a library to read and write TrueType fonts in Ruby.

    Tables supported are :

        - Cmap *
        - Cvt *
        - Fpgm *
        - Gasp
        - Glyf
        - Head
        - Hhea
        - Hmtx
        - Kern *
        - OS/2
        - Post *
        - Prep *
        - Vhea
        - Vmtx

    (Tables marked with an * are only partially supported)

Requirements
------------

    Ruby >= 1.8.0:              http://www.ruby-lang.org

Install 
-------

    # ruby setup.rb

Documentation
-------------

    $ rdoc --main "TTFFont::TTF::File"

Tools
-----

See tools/README.

